document_notes.text:
This update for python fixes the following issues:

- CVE-2019-20907: Avoid a possible infinite loop caused by specifically crafted tarballs (bsc#1174091).

notes.text: In Lib/tarfile.py in Python through 3.8.3, an attacker is able to craft a TAR archive leading to an infinite loop when opened by tarfile.open, because _proc_pax lacks header validation.
